After the ceremony,

00:36:35.440 --> 00:36:37.220
His Majesty will hold the Grand Festival

00:36:37.240 --> 00:36:37.980
at the Hua'e Xianghui Tower,

00:36:37.980 --> 00:36:39.170
banqueting ministers and their families.

00:36:39.400 --> 00:36:41.340
Consort Shu will also perform a dance for His Majesty.

